\iex (We have not yet translated 22:21—23:29.)
\c 24
\s1 David shamed Saul properly
\p 
\v 1 Another time Saul \w and|strong="H1732"\w* \w his|strong="H1732"\w* \w soldiers|strong="H5927"\w* \w went|strong="H5927"\w* \w to|strong="H5927"\w* fight \w with|strong="H3427"\w* \w the|strong="H5927"\w* Philistia mob. \w After|strong="H5927"\w* \w they|strong="H8033"\w* \w came|strong="H5927"\w* \w back|strong="H5927"\w*, somebody told \w him|strong="H5927"\w* \w this|strong="H5927"\w* story, “\w David|strong="H1732"\w*’s mob \w are|strong="H8033"\w* \w in|strong="H3427"\w* \w the|strong="H5927"\w* desert \w at|strong="H3427"\w* \w En-Gedi|strong="H5872"\w*.”
\v 2 \w So|strong="H1961"\w* \w Saul|strong="H7586"\w* got 3,000 \w of|strong="H4057"\w* \w his|strong="H1732"\w* best soldiers together \w from|strong="H7725"\w* \w every|strong="H7725"\w* \w place|strong="H1961"\w* \w in|strong="H7725"\w* Israel. \w And|strong="H7725"\w* \w they|strong="H7586"\w* \w went|strong="H1732"\w* \w off|strong="H7725"\w* \w to|strong="H7725"\w* \w look|strong="H2009"\w* \w for|strong="H1961"\w* \w David|strong="H1732"\w* \w and|strong="H7725"\w* \w his|strong="H1732"\w* men \w in|strong="H7725"\w* \w the|strong="H7725"\w* hill country, near \w a|strong="H3068"\w* \w place|strong="H1961"\w* called \em the rocks of the wild goats\em*.
