\p 
\v 1 \w One|strong="H3808"\w* day, some men \w from|strong="H6440"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* place called Zif \w went|strong="H1732"\w* \w to|strong="H5921"\w* see \w Saul|strong="H7586"\w* \w at|strong="H5921"\w* \w his|strong="H1732"\w* place \w at|strong="H5921"\w* \w Gibeah|strong="H1390"\w*. \w They|strong="H5921"\w* said, “\w David|strong="H1732"\w*’s mob \w are|strong="H6440"\w* \w hiding|strong="H5641"\w* \w in|strong="H5921"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* cave \w at|strong="H5921"\w* \w the|strong="H6440"\w* \w hill|strong="H1389"\w* called Hakilah \w near|strong="H6440"\w* \w Jeshimon|strong="H3452"\w* town.”\x * \xo 26:1 \xt Psalm 54\x*
